communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org

[On 14 Nov 2019, ProMED-mail first posted on 3 cases of O157 infection occurring in the Eau Claire, WI area. Since the last CDC post on 24 Nov 2019, 2 days ago, 27 more cases have been recognized. It is not that the 27 cases occurred in the 2 days but, rather, that they occurred previously and have now, through testing, been shown to be associated with the outbreak. We await additional updates on the total in Wisconsin and nationwide. - Mod.LL

HealthMap/ProMED map available at:
United States: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=6799440,106]
